ITEM 1A. RISK FACTORS
In addition to the factors discussed elsewhere in this Form 10-K, this section discusses important factors which could
cause actual results or events to differ materially from those contained in any forward-looking statements made by us.
The order of presentation is not necessarily indicative of the level of risk that each factor poses to us. Any of these
factors could have a material adverse effect on our business, results of operations, financial condition, or stock price.
Our operations could also be affected by other factors that are presently unknown to us or not considered significant.
